{"tid":1451604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【人面獸心】呢頭見有人爆眼，嗰頭呀葉國興即刻想用錢塞住人把口","createTime":"2019-08-11T19:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T20:16:48.000Z","uid":134134,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8ef1e86d8e1cd69f4429cf8f760d09d61ed68117","tid":1451604,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ounGywh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FounGywh.jpg&h=8bac48aa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n援助？援你老母！係咪想洗街坊腦，啲人出嚟示威係因為經濟不景？呢頭見有個女仔俾狗爆眼，嗰頭你就即刻想用錢塞住人把口，洗太平地？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jGCy86k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjGCy86k.jpg&h=a2b6b896&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n持住自己同時係業委會主席，自己俾自己喺業委會塊版，宣傳區議員辦事處活動。越權一定好開心啦。宣傳品唔使受上頭監管，鍾意貼邊就貼邊，自己批自己係咪呀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E08RVPb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE08RVPb.jpg&h=f1bcf4cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢條撚屌做咗25年土皇帝，政績乏善可陳，態度不求有功，但求無過。剩係識借沙士刷鞋打飛機。實事呢？滅下蚊，關注下水渠咁囉。淘大對出空地，丟空四五年先起個公園，公園入面水機俾小朋友飲啲水，咁多年嚟都係臭嘅。橋底幾年前話翻新，點知封到今日。泳池殘舊，救生員不足，無關注過。<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有光明正大俾政府喺淘大條路起監控鏡頭</span>，好彩譚文豪即刻call人拆咗佢。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Kowloon Bayer！一票不投葉國興！</span></span>"},{"pid":"d4e3617aebe4056a7b96e349833a13446a6c8d50","tid":1451604,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:37:57.000Z","msg":"同場加映：銅鑼灣有狗扮示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V-cA30W1308&amp;feature=share&amp;fbclid=IwAR1EjJn6Z1QOsXUBAFasyjTc7-O_usOzlxs-9bDu9TzKfeKNbeTX0Q2FXFc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DV-cA30W1308%26feature%3Dshare%26fbclid%3DIwAR1EjJn6Z1QOsXUBAFasyjTc7-O_usOzlxs-9bDu9TzKfeKNbeTX0Q2FXFc&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=81ddab0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V-cA30W1308&amp;feature=share&amp;fbclid=IwAR1EjJn6Z1QOsXUBAFasyjTc7-O_usOzlxs-9bDu9TzKfeKNbeTX0Q2FXFc</a>"},{"pid":"c5e6907c031852f7781ddf0812b0ba7e49194ec1","tid":1451604,"uid":103476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:38:07.000Z","msg":"係時候學識反擊打狗啦！非常重要，借位一用<br />\n<br />\n致所有比狗打而想反抗嘅前線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1448193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1448193</a>"},{"pid":"78ef7a2d75d525f3a963cb20bd8aa167f36e690f","tid":1451604,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WvA8X9k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWvA8X9k.jpg&h=91d62bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8O22A0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8O22A0.jpg&h=d9f2f23e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e73994eb4ab7916e2cd13fde156ff0f04fad7f4d","tid":1451604,"uid":220438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:16:48.000Z","msg":"孽瘤一早叫政府派錢啦 佢而家先死出黎講 遲唔遲啲呀"}]}